title: Couple With Heart: Person, Medium Skin Tone, Person, Default Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Two Women Holding Hands with Heart
description: Represents a romantic couple consisting of two women, one with a medium skin tone and the other with the default skin tone. It symbolizes love, partnership, and commitment between two women.
apple_vendor_description: This delightful couple emoji on Apple devices features a woman with a medium skin tone, lovingly embracing a heart symbol rendered with Apple's signature glossy sheen and soft, rounded edges. The realistic lighting on their forms suggests a tender connection and warmth, embodying affection and a deep bond.  It's a beautiful representation of romantic love and partnership, often used to celebrate relationships or express heartfelt emotions on Apple devices.
